snippet.title: Jay-Z And BeyoncE Celebrate 40/40 Club Anniversary, Johny Depp/Amber Heard, Drake More...
snippet.description: Jay-z and BeyoncE celebrate the anniversary of the 40/40 club with a host of friends as guest. Ne Ne Leakes husband Gregg Leakes is dying from colon cancer and is transitioning to the other side as she watches in sorrow. Johnny Depp's celebrating his return to the film industry while Amber Heard is drowning her self inflicted sorrows with wine and friends. And while they were searching for other so called victims or accusers of Depp they found out that her father was arrested and charged with animal cruelty and fighting pit bull dogs. Drake's CLB is releasing on Friday with a different album look and lil nas x is trolling it and trying to bring notice to his own album. #JayZ #BeyoncE #Drake #JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #CLB #40/40 Club
